---
title: Chipotle-Glazed BBQ Halloumi with Garlic Cauli-Broccoli Rice & Charred Corn Salsa
description: Give halloumi a dash of flair with a glaze of chipotle sauce and tangy barbecue seasoning for a melding of robust flavours. Then, ramp up your dish with a dollop of creamy mayonnaise and a wholesome serving of garlicky cauli-broccoli rice. This one’s an exciting ride from start to finish.

